  "title": "Anthropic 增长主管：工程师越多，产品经理越稀缺丨 Lenny's Podcast",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzcxMDA5NTI0OA==&mid=2247485639&idx=1&sn=e24dc5f07f1e301ca081fa27df065dd5",
  "date": "2026-04-07 12:11:00",
